title: Yodel Kid Mason Ramsey Stops By & Critiques Lunchbox's Yodeling Skills + Bobby Opens Up About An Emotional Moment He Had
itunes:title: Yodel Kid Mason Ramsey Stops By & Critiques Lunchbox's Yodeling Skills + Bobby Opens Up About An Emotional Moment He Had
description:
The Yodel Kid, Mason Ramsey, stops by the show to talk about life after going viral, his new song "Famous," and even critiques Lunchbox's yodeling ability. Bobby opens up about something that made him emotional recently. Also, the show shares their recent Time Marches On moments!
